Honestly, I don't think I would be an Owl City fan if my first song was Fireflies. Don't get me wrong: I like that song, but I don't think it would have made me want to look up any more of Adam's music if I just heard that with nothing else around it. So, I'll forever be grateful to the one high school student who drove me to school in 8th grade, constantly playing Maybe I'm Dreaming and Ocean Eyes in her car. If I didn't hear the Maybe I'm Dreaming version of The Saltwater Room (my first Owl City song), I don't think I would be a fan today.
